## Hitting the fgets Limit

the problem is that `fgets()` only reads:

```asm
movl $0x200, 0x4(%esp)
```

which means:

```text
512 bytes maximum
```

even if i try:

```bash
python -c 'print "A"*134513828' | ./level5 | wc -c
```

i only get:

```text
511
```

characters.

so i cannot send 134 million characters directly.

